                                "stop": 10.78,
                                "byte_start": 73975,
                                "byte_stop": 117129,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 89-1821, Stevens versus Department of the Treasury will be announced by Justice Blackmun."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 10.78,
                        "stop": 96.549,
